<h1>Name</h1>
<p>clearchart -- Reset all values in the chart system.</p>
<h1>Synopsis</h1>
<p>bool <b>chart->clearchart</b> ( )</p>
<h1>Description</h1>
<p>This method clears all series and values from the chart
system in preparation for a new chart. If you place multiple
charts in a single PDF, you should call this method after each
call to chart->place_chart()</p>
<h1>Examples</h1>
<pre>
$pdf->chart->place_chart($page, 10, 10, 300, 200, 'line');
$pdf->chart->clearchart();
</pre>
